WIN.description: The 'WIN' block ends the game when the player's character (or 'YOU') touches it.
WIN.last_rationale: Makes the subject block win the game when touched.

YOU.description: Refers to the player's character. It can interact with other blocks, push, pull, and change rules when adjacent to them.
YOU.last_rationale: The 'YOU' block represents the player's character, which is the primary agent for interacting with the game world.
